title: Alberto, Rangers beat Blue Jays in 14th, lead ALDS 2-0
text:
> Texas Alberto, Rangers beat Blue Jays in 14th, lead ALDS 2-0 Texas Rangers, from left to right, Hanser Alberto, Shin-Soo Choo, and Rougned Odor celebrate Choo scoring during the first inning in Game 2 of baseballs American League Division Series in Toronto on Friday, Oct. 9, 2015. (Darren Calabrese/The Canadian Press via AP)
